    inputLockDuration: 0
    autoContinue: 0
    autoContinueDelay: 1
  - speakerName: "Uncle H\u1EA3i"
    content: "V\xEC v\u1EADy, ng\xE0y mai sinh vi\xEAn kh\xF4ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
      v\xE0o C7 v\u1EDBi m\u1EE5c \u0111\xEDch nghi\xEAn c\u1EE9u."
